pcie-access (0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Generic PCI stub driver for userspace BAR access via ioctl.
  * Supports MSI-X/MSI/INTx interrupt monitoring.
  * 64-bit MMIO access on CONFIG_64BIT architectures.
  * Safe hot-unplug via kref + rw_semaphore.
  * Miscdevice-based char device per PCI function.
  * Userspace CLI tool with domain addressing support.

 -- Maciej Grochowski <maciej.grochowski@pm.me>  Sun, 23 Mar 2026 11:30:00 -0700
